name: Symbiotic 8
body: This is a debugged and improved version of SV-COMP 2021 Symbiotic 8.

name: SV-COMP 21 version
body:
This release is a fixed version of Symbiotic that competed in SV-COMP 2021. The unfixed version is available from the competition's archives. 

The fixes are:
 - fix of slicing for termination category
 - fix of handling fpclassify in slowbeast
 - generating trivial witnesses for 'true' answers from slowbeast

Slowbeast used is: https://gitlab.fi.muni.cz/xchalup4/slowbeast/-/tree/svcomp21-v1

name: Symbiotic 4.0.0
body:

- fix paths to generated witnesses & few small bugfixes

name: 3.0.7-pre (RC)
body:
- support memsafety properties
- get rid of external scripts (rewritten into the python)
- update to LLVM 3.8.1
- slicer bugfixes & improvements
- use more aggressive optimizations

name: Symbiotic 3.0.2
body:
### Changelog:

```
* more user-friendly output and more options
* few improvements to svc15
* more precise slicing (fixed bugs that made the slicing unprecise)
* lots of slicer critical bugfixes
* few new tests
```
